{"tid":1193311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳]有心做運動唔洗行太耐做熱身","createTime":"2019-06-09T00:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T07:33:16.000Z","uid":31539,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ee685f8b1a4e93e915af247824491e535014c0","tid":1193311,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:11:24.000Z","msg":"今日雖然好好天大家好有運動mood<br />\n但係如果有心做劇烈運動<br />\n就冇乜需要大熱天時行幾個鐘晒力啦<br />\n去定想做運動既地方<br />\n揾個冷氣位涼下 臨開波先做熱身動作<br />\n落到場先夠力架嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然個諗住行完當做夠運動d weak可以唔洗理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天氣報告話今晚落雨<br />\n預留得耐記得帶雨衣/更換衣物<br />\n特別襪,以前出去中環踢波就係冇,醃到香港腳灰甲齊<br />\n祝各位可以操fit d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287fb4b9c6e45c6b6e9f1152e53f08d3725291ca","tid":1193311,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:13:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f75eba33595998e8164ee9e11f449296928da5d","tid":1193311,"uid":148987,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:13:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提防糾察散水篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"e73a0222eaafb9305b12fd9f5848ac216398c8bf","tid":1193311,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:23:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd4cbb191a74940